{"tid":537983,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[認真討論] 一句到尾 李榮浩定薛梓謙？","createTime":"2018-01-23T08:03:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-23T10:42:24.000Z","uid":130369,"like":30,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3f6669c8ba8432696b8be33a925627870153c95d","tid":537983,"uid":130369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T08:03:17.000Z","msg":"相信好多人都會將佢地比較 我就中意佢地唔同既特色 對我黎講<br />\n<br />\n薛: 寫得好入心入肺 真係冇啲經歷都寫唔出呢啲詞 佢既歌聽第一次就會上癮 不過我就唔可以狂聽 驚聽得太多就冇乜feel <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n李: 用好淺白既詞 去表達成首歌意思 平淡得黎又好描寫到個種心情 好似有個人陪住你過咁 開頭聽第一次 會覺得麻麻地 再聽多幾次就發覺真係好好聽 不停loop<br />\n<br />\n佢地兩個既分別就好似wyman同林夕咁 各有各好！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你地又點揀呢？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 李<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 薛"},{"pid":"c467c5236491dc83ce0dc04571a997c556d81060","tid":537983,"uid":130369,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T08:10:19.000Z","msg":"李榮浩個人推介:<br />\n老街<br />\n不將就<br />\n就這樣<br />\n歌謠<br />\n祝你幸福<br />\n<br />\n薛梓謙個人推介:<br />\n曖昧<br />\n認真的雪<br />\n剛剛好<br />\n動物世界"},{"pid":"769ee673fe1838d02edb9c978466ff59a79c2489","tid":537983,"uid":166320,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T08:17:08.000Z","msg":"梓你老母咩"},{"pid":"5acea69ec1e20e5fe99dfb7d943ddfd3663bb572","tid":537983,"uid":40575,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T08:18:55.000Z","msg":"屌你人地叫咩名都未撚知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f80f6b88f7f7554ee38e4593592279dc291c011f","tid":537983,"uid":130369,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T08:20:46.000Z","msg":"薛之謙<br />\n自膠一打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkg